
- docs - http://hugo.spf13.com/overview/quickstart/

install
------------------
- install hugo
  go get github.com/spf13/hugo

- themes
   git clone --recursive https://github.com/spf13/hugoThemes themes

basics
------------------

- make a new file
   hugo new post/first.md


- dev server

   hugo server --theme=hyde --buildDrafts
